text: Castiarina vegetaCastiarina vegeta is a beetle (Order Coleoptera) in the Family Buprestidae, otherwise known as jewel beetles. The species was described by Hope in 1847. == Citation== Castiarina vegeta == Distribution == South Australia, Victoria. ==References== *Barker, S., 2006: Castiarina: Australia's richest jewel beetle genus.
